Robert Emmett Keane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Emmett_Keane 0 Robert Emmett Keane (March 4, 1883 – July 2, 1981) was an American actor of both the stage and screen. He was also known professionally by the names: Emmett Keane, Robert Keane, R. Emmett Keane, and Robert E. Keane.
